00:00:14.431 --> 00:00:16.057 position:50% align:center
[MEISEI A]
Over to the left!

00:00:18.351 --> 00:00:19.811 position:50% align:center
So close!

00:00:19.894 --> 00:00:21.813 position:50% align:center
[HAIJIMA]
Miles away more like it.

00:00:27.068 --> 00:00:29.320 position:50% align:center
[HAIJIMA] Three blockers
on the left again.

