but you showed up.

00:11:56.257 --> 00:11:59.844 position:50% align:center
Also, that warm up routine
of yours is absolute trash.

00:11:59.928 --> 00:12:02.263 position:50% align:center
We're gonna start
with some proper stretches.

00:12:02.347 --> 00:12:03.973 position:50% align:center
Stay there.

00:12:12.107 --> 00:12:14.317 position:50% align:center
[KUROBA]
In math, you got a 95?

00:12:14.401 --> 00:12:17.362 position:50% align:center
And a 99 in social studies?

00:12:17.445 --> 00:12:19.948 position:50% align:center
But what's this?
A 30 in Japanese?

00:12:20.031 --> 00:12:21.408 position:50% align:center
Would you shut up?

00:12:21.491 --> 00:12:23.535 position:50% align:center
How long are you gonna keep
goin' on about my grades?

00:12:23.618 --> 00:12:24.786 position:50% align:center
[KUROBA]
Tryin' to kill me?

00:12:24.869 --> 00:12:26.705 position:50% align:center
Like you're one to talk.

00:12:26.788 --> 00:12:29.749 position:50% align:center
A 42 in math.
Social studies, a D.

00:12:29.833 --> 00:12:31.626 position:50% align:center
Wanna compare test scores, fine.

00:12:31.710 --> 00:12:33.003 position:50% align:center
What about in Japanese then?

00:12:33.086 --> 00:12:34.713 position:50% align:center
Which one of us made an 87?

00:12:34.796 --> 00:12:37.257 position:50% align:center
Ow! Take it easy!

00:12:38.216 --> 00:12:39.509 position:50% align:center
